title: Moby’s best live moments from Cercle Odyssey are out!

author: Cercle
description:
Having Moby with us for two nights in Los Angeles felt unreal, especially knowing this would be his only live performance of the year. He turned Cercle Odyssey into a tidal wave of sound: raw, powerful and unstoppable letting that little rave kid inside all of us witness the iconic tracks that shaped our childhood.
